message.content:
To His True World, as you call it, we come to die,'

Lily-yo said, doubtingly. The Captive with the

fleshless jew said, 'The grub of the tigerfly thinks

it dies when it changes into a tigerfly.' 'You are still

young,' said the Chief Captive. 'You begin newly here.

Where are your souls?' Lily-yo and Tla looked at

each other. In their flight from the twilight they had

heedlessly thrown down their souls.
